These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, canadian, thai, colombian
1. the spanish is on the right of the colombian##1
2. the canadian is somewhere between the thai and the colombian##7
3. the thai is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Nationality   | thai | canadian | colombian | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, oliveros, montecristo, blend
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere between the oliveros-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##7
3. the montecristo-smoker is between the oliveros-smoker and the blend-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | aristoff | blend | montecristo | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different games are played: domino, scrabble, monopoly, canasta
1. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the person playing scrabble##7
3. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | domino | scrabble | canasta | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, golf, climbing, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's sport is golf##7
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Sport   | climbing | snowboarding | sailing | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, cola, lemonade
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
4. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person drinking lemonade##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Beverage   | cola | milk | sprite | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, zucchini, blueberry, grapefruit
1. the person eating garlic is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating zucchini##7
2. the person eating blueberry is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person eating grapefruit##7
3. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
4. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Food   | grapefruit | blueberry | garlic | zucchini |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, traveling, sudoku, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is baking##7
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is traveling##7
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Hobby   | baking | rock-climbing | sudoku | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, magic-tricks, puzzles, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | singing | magic-tricks | video-games | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-9::.
4 different games are played: snooker, domino, whist, poker
1. the person playing whist is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing poker is somewhere between the person playing domino and the person playing whist##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Game   | whist | snooker | poker | domino |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-10::.
