.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, october, september
1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in october##2
2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in september##7
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |  3   |    4    |
| Birthday   | september | february | october | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-12::.
