2. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3    |      4       |
| Hobby   | collecting | photography | camping | skydiving |

