.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-17::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, snake, rabbit, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the snake##7
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |
| Pet   | snake | turtle | guinea-pig | rabbit |

