.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, skiing, baseball, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##5
2. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7
